tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE WeatherData (
  date DATE,
  temperature FLOAT,
  humidity FLOAT,
  rainfall FLOAT,
  wind_speed FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE weather_data (
    city STRING,
    date DATE,
    temperature FLOAT,
    humidity FLOAT,
    precipitation FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE crop_yield (
    crop_name STRING,
    date DATE,
    yield INT,
    temperature_requirement FLOAT,
    humidity_requirement FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE CropData (
    crop_name VARCHAR,
    crop_type VARCHAR,
    planting_date DATE,
    harvest_date DATE,
    estimated_yield FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE Weather_Data (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    location VARCHAR(255),
    date DATE,
    temperature FLOAT,
    humidity FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE Crop_Data (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    crop_name VARCHAR(255),
    planting_date DATE,
    harvest_date DATE,
    yield_estimate FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE Soil_Data (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    location VARCHAR(255),
    nitrogen_level FLOAT,
    phosphorus_level FLOAT,
    potassium_level FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE Field_Data (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    location VARCHAR(255),
    field_area FLOAT,
    crop_id INT,
    soil_id INT
)

CREATE TABLE Prediction (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    date DATE,
    predicted_yield FLOAT,
    actual_yield FLOAT,
    crop_id INT
)
